---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="關於我們">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 pb-32">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 tracking-wider">關於慧陶香</h1>
      <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-brand-500 mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div class="order-2 lg:order-1 relative">
        <div class="aspect-w-4 aspect-h-3 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl relative z-10">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1596756860368-80e9a44c5ce7?w=1000&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="陶藝大師" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
        </div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-8 -left-8 w-64 h-64 bg-brand-100 rounded-full z-0 opacity-50 blur-3xl"></div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="order-1 lg:order-2 space-y-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 leading-snug">
          傳承歷史的溫度，<br/>揉合現代的設計美學。
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          慧陶香企業社成立於二十年前，由一群熱愛陶土與傳統工藝的陶藝師共同創立。我們深信，器皿不僅僅是盛裝食物的工具，更是乘載生活記憶與情感的橋樑。
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          堅持選用天然陶土，搭配獨家窯燒工序，使每件作品都擁有獨特的色澤與質地。除了手工陶器販售，我們更開設手作課程，期望將這份感動傳遞給更多熱愛生活的人。
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-8 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200">
          <div>
            <div class="text-4xl font-black text-brand-600 mb-2">20+</div>
            <div class="text-gray-500 font-medium">年工藝傳承</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-4xl font-black text-brand-600 mb-2">1,500+</div>
            <div class="text-gray-500 font-medium">學員體驗人數</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>